%% Diagram: How an insertion shifts boundaries under fixed-size vs content-defined chunking
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart TB
    O1["Original<br/>A B C D · E F G H · I J K L"]

    F1["Fixed-size, after inserting X<br/>X A B C · D E F G · H I J K · L _ _ _<br/><br/>Every chunk hash changes.<br/>≈0% dedup vs original."]

    C1["CDC, after inserting X<br/>X A B C D · E F G H · I J K L<br/><br/>Chunks 2 and 3 byte-identical.<br/>≈67% dedup vs original."]

    O1 --> F1
    O1 --> C1

    style O1 fill:#e1f5fe
    style F1 fill:#ffebee
    style C1 fill:#e8f5e9
